abstract: Brandt Snedeker wins Pebble Beach National Pro-Am tournament with 265.
lead_paragraph: Brandt Snedeker broke his own scoring record and won the Pebble Beach National Pro-Am in California for the second time in three years.

headline.main: Snedeker Breaks Mark in Pro-Am Win
